{"tid":413204,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[中學回憶]容易諗咸濕野笑一定要入","createTime":"2017-09-25T09:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T08:40:24.000Z","uid":87937,"like":1016,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a137d3fe3594c68dbf1d9443e4727fc2753dd27","tid":413204,"uid":87937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:56:19.000Z","msg":"中學一定會有升學組既老師<br />\n會抽一個星期係周會時間分享心得<br />\n中六既時候 有個女老師同我地班講學業前途<br />\n你都知平時周會一定用黎補眠<br />\n本身大家都半睡狀態<br />\n好多廢話你唔會想入耳<br />\n但以下既對話 好深刻咁記住左<br />\n每次諗返都會笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢無啦啦攞自己個女做例子<br />\n<br />\n女老師：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n男同學：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：好心你地班人比啲心機讀書啦<br />\n考完DSE之後就要準備揀科揀系<br />\n好既科好既系係要靠努力爭取<br />\n我個女當年就係考得好揀左個好系<br />\n你地知唔知 幾多人爭住入我個女個系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個系好搶手好多人想入都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：(玩野咁問)我都好想入你個女個系<br />\n點樣先可以入到佢個系？<br />\n你會唔會唔比我地入佢個系？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知個老師回應仲爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：點會唔比你地入佢個系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有本事既可以隨便入囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個女個系真係好特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢個系係好深入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係要好努力先入到佢個系<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每次諗起呢個對話都覺得自己好咸濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95408f14858d746e54b0468892f9915fe16fba0","tid":413204,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f94f7396b83abe85a4bd1ac7e5ce676165f8a90","tid":413204,"uid":48791,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:07:06.000Z","msg":"...."},{"pid":"733faa0e4cfdcaa6b7f39e1bbf84c81ce72fbf5d","tid":413204,"uid":87937,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係懶好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef3fd6472d879451da01946bcad13271f90440b","tid":413204,"uid":32298,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"🦐🦐🦐"},{"pid":"012ec90c8cc0a9d3b1fd2d806a2c960a8146656d","tid":413204,"uid":140280,"like":15,"dislike":320,"score":-305,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:11:41.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},{"pid":"fb4f041c840cdf6122336b012b1cdad960966652","tid":413204,"uid":66604,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>系你老母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28360ebf6bc509114f7e5d8d8fa8ee26196310fb","tid":413204,"uid":53254,"like":86,"dislike":4,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得這個ok<br />\n但笑唔出"},{"pid":"ad7863553cb623b121de1b64222c1653a48850e2","tid":413204,"uid":53278,"like":183,"dislike":7,"score":176,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"巴打唔好灰！<br />\n今次唔好笑姐 下次努力！"},{"pid":"8a0ed3ccd7b9582c7e9b45074e372b0e6a5f86ed","tid":413204,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:21:06.000